Automated Phishing Triage

### Flow (ASCII Diagram)

+-------------------------+
| New Email Reported (SOC)|
+-------------------------+
           |
           v
+-------------------------+
| Extract IOCs (URLs, IPs)|
+-------------------------+
           |
           v
+-------------------------+
| Threat Intel Lookup     |
| (VT, OTX, MISP, etc.)   |
+-------------------------+
           |
           v
+-------------------------+
| Reputation Scoring      |
+-------------------------+
           |
           v
+-------------------------+
| Auto-Tag Email +        |
| Analyst Notification    |
+-------------------------+

**Benefit:** cuts phishing triage time from ~15 min to <2 min per case, ensuring analysts only review high-risk emails.
